original: Östman, Carl Gustaf, civilingenjör SVR, hyggnadschef, Norrköping, f. 11/7/92 i Örnsköldsvik av Gustaf Ö. o. Augusta Backman. G. 1. 18 m. Elsa-Lena Lundström, d. 46; 2. 48 m. Lisa Margareta Bergström. Barn: Bengt f. 23, odönt. kand. — Stud :ex. i Umeå 11, avg:ex. fr. KTH (V) 16. Utr. stud:res. Anst. v. A-B Ing:-firman Unander & Jonson i Sthlm 16-18, vattenledn :ing. v. Norrköp. stads byggn :kont. 18, ibyggn :chef i Norrköp. sed. 42 (41). V. ordf. i Norrköp. auto-mobil- o. flygkl., ordf. i Norrköp. modell- o. segelflygkl. 35-43, led. av styr.
translated: Östman, Carl Gustaf, engineer SVR, construction manager, Norrköping, b. 11/7/92 in Örnsköldsvik to Gustaf Ö. and Augusta Backman. Married 1st in 18 m. Elsa-Lena Lundström, d. 46; 2nd in 48 m. Lisa Margareta Bergström. Children: Bengt b. 23, deceased candidate. Studied: exam in Umeå 11, graduated from KTH (V) 16. Studied abroad. Employed by A-B Ing:-firman Unander & Jonson in Stockholm 16-18, water supply engineer at Norrköping city building office 18, construction manager in Norrköping since 42 (41). Vice-chairman of Norrköping automobile and aviation club, chairman of Norrköping model and gliding club 35-43, member of the board.
